{
  "texts": [
    "Such collaboration could improve the feedback's expression by offering alternative phrasing options to avoid text sounding repetitive and by rewording feedback for clarity.",
    "Educators' handling of sensitive data also needs to be addressed, as highlighted by Zhai (2022).",
    "However, the participants also noted that AI did not always match an individual staff member's style.",
    "For optimal AI performance, they recommended an initial human review of feedback to align AI with academic language and subject-specific terms, and fine-tuning AI to mimic the style and tone of the individual academic.",
    "This discussion highlights the need for future research to investigate the technical and ethical challenges in the higher education sector on how AI can be integrated into the feedback process of existing educational frameworks that support student engagement."
  ]
}